snippet.title: 15 Defense - Steam Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Play 15 Defense on: http://store.steampowered.com/app/599090/

Fight them all! This game gets you plunged into a tough fight on the bottom of some imaginary sea. Watch it out, enemies never sleep! Resist their attacks and improve your survival time by upgrading your skills and talents.
